{"tid":1689971,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"抗爭人數減少嘅一個重要原因︰缺乏創意","createTime":"2019-11-03T05:52:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-03T11:19:13.000Z","uid":108757,"like":99,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":54,"replies":[{"pid":"21d2d8c863ad765115ee1b396820b0384fca5641","tid":1689971,"uid":108757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T05:52:37.000Z","msg":"8月第一次人鏈，個個嘅反應係︰人鏈？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好！<br />\n第二次人鏈︰人鏈？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好！<br />\n第十次人鏈︰<span style=\"color: red;\">又</span>人鏈？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n第N次人鏈︰<span style=\"color: red;\">又</span>人鏈？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n連豬話︰<span style=\"color: red;\">又</span>嚟？唔好喇掛<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n點解外國傳媒會調走記者離開香港，點解活動會愈來愈少人出，因為同一種活動做得多就會悶，<span style=\"color: red;\">無咗新聞價值</span>。同理，遊行、集會、唱歌、快閃所有嘅抗爭活動，熱度同關注度都會隨時間減少，如果要保持熱度，一定要為抗爭<span style=\"color: red;\">加入新元素</span>，第一可以突破樽頸位，第二可以保持關注度，有助本地同國際戰線。<br />\n<br />\n點樣增加新元素同新鮮感？需要全民一齊思考，唔好怕無厘頭，一開始人鏈其實都好尷尬，做咗出嚟其實效果非常好。<br />\n1. Cross-over<br />\n將現有抗爭手法集合一齊，變成一種新手法。例如和你SHOP (罷買+唱歌+和你塞)、節日贈慶(罷買+遊行)、午飯快閃(遊行+快閃)<br />\n<br />\n2. 發掘全新抗爭概念<br />\n分析現有抗爭手法，搵出盲點，創造全新手法。例如和你返工(抗爭時間改變)、V煞日(抗爭公布模式改變)、之前嘅修頓LBJ籃球賽(針對某件事發大嚟搞)<br />\n<br />\n[突破] 如果你覺得一早話哂畀班狗知幾點邊到集合好on9嘅 即刻同我入哂嚟<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1689789\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1689789</a><br />\n<br />\n（突破樽頸）請返工日子  早上抗爭   真正影響民生<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1689729\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1689729</a><br />\n<br />\n【國際NBA戰線】10月15修頓,掀動全球抗共<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1651826\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1651826</a><br />\n<br />\n拋磚引玉，未來可以舉行︰<br />\n1. Stand with Journalist, Stand with Press集會 (針對警察侵犯第四權此事)<br />\n2. Connect全球不同宗教遊行(針對警方侮辱宗教)<br />\n3. 光復連儂牆行動(集會+文宣)<br />\n4. 守護投票站行動<br />\n<br />\n香港人最有創意，香港人最需要創意。<br />\n大家集思廣益<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/s0cSF6F.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fs0cSF6F.gif&h=32f64e29&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2bbdcb7b4a16e65268c0b42973bf5d1be3c72fd4","tid":1689971,"uid":108757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T05:56:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"248fb74efdf8984c4c48bc6581f1d4f83c7e90a2","tid":1689971,"uid":108757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T05:58:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a709ca7561167b7a6b1f942c59a96e746f1c6d7","tid":1689971,"uid":284949,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T06:02:27.000Z","msg":"幫推"},{"pid":"80b2f6f82708dbf37cdc57bad0952c153a2a64ac","tid":1689971,"uid":108757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T06:05:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"557fa8d9efbb439908c9295a402215903477d5f4","tid":1689971,"uid":2024,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T06:07:37.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"41cec655f198854ea83131e0c4d2a0e2247cb213","tid":1689971,"uid":324225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T06:08:27.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f892dc69797a93b8ef7e5466e5cbdac44f245ab","tid":1689971,"uid":324225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T06:08:41.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0dbe134d255a03a7e8dfe795e2d348d387f86e1","tid":1689971,"uid":100714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy"