c=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f1f8a1cbc1acae4fced0627380acfa50b21c24d","tid":1689971,"uid":108757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T07:56:18.000Z","msg":"[突破瓶頸]新活動&quot;和你熄&quot; 全港關燈10分鐘有冇得諗???<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1690128\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1690128</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"d0515c6ae508093d7f7278690f7fb755fe6ebbec","tid":1689971,"uid":181362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T07:58:28.000Z","msg":"可以諗啲和理非容易入場既活動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"29f2d77f919709b4569ff4eb5add3a34694c7026","tid":1689971,"uid":246242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T08:01:17.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"1f5d67dca24bed1e558487061571c0711d52392f","tid":1689971,"uid":318632,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T08:02:07.000Z","msg":"最新狗戰術 及解決方法<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1690138\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1690138</a>"},{"pid":"b42798238c8161f3916f684dcb727d22fcf9319d","tid":1689971,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T08:19:28.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"583b127152d224341732bb12adeebdd918b9cc0e","tid":1689971,"uid":84614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T08:38:52.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1357e7172503cc63d62b4e02796bbbde2cd56a34","tid":1689971,"uid":55955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T08:40:27.000Z","msg":"新風向係叫人如果唔勇武就不如唔好做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b4043730e3cb147674820282a3081792a6a964c","tid":1689971,"uid":317188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"21d2d8c863ad765115ee1b396820b0384fca5641","tid":1689971,"uid":108757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T05:52:37.000Z","msg":"8月第一次人鏈，個個嘅反應係︰人鏈？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好！<br />\n第二次人鏈︰人鏈？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好！<br />\n第十次人鏈︰<span style=\"color: red;\">又</span>人鏈？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n第N次人鏈︰<span style=\"color: red;\">又</span>人鏈？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n連豬話︰<span style=\"color: red;\">又</span>嚟？唔好喇掛<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n點解外國傳媒會調走記者離開香港，點解活動會愈來愈少人出，因為同一種活動做得多就會悶，<span style=\"color: red;\">無咗新聞價值</span>。同理，遊行、集會、唱歌、快閃所有嘅抗爭活動，熱度同關注度都會隨時間減少，如果要保持熱度，一定要為抗爭<span style=\"color: red;\">加入新元素</span>，第一可以突破樽頸位，第二可以保持關注度，有助本地同國際戰線。<br />\n<br />\n點樣增加新元素同新鮮感？需要全民一齊思考，唔好怕無厘頭，一開始人鏈其實都好尷尬，做咗出嚟其實效果非常好。<br />\n1. Cross-over<br />\n將現有抗爭手法集合一齊，變成一種新手法。例如和你SHOP (罷買+唱歌+和你塞)、節日贈慶(罷買+遊行)、午飯快閃(遊行+快閃)<br />\n<br />\n2. 發掘全新抗爭概念<br />\n分析現有抗爭手法，搵出盲點，創造全新手法。例如和你返工(抗爭時間改變)、V煞日(抗爭公布模式改變)、之前嘅修頓LBJ籃球賽(針對某件事發大嚟搞)<br />\n<br />\n[突破] 如果你覺得一早話哂畀班狗知幾點邊到集合好on9嘅 即刻同我入哂嚟<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1689789\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1689789</a><br />\n<br />\n（突破樽頸）請返工日子  早上抗爭   真正影響民生<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1689729\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1689729</a><br />\n<br />\n【國際NBA戰線】10月15修頓,掀動全球抗共<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1651826\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1651826</a><br />\n<br />\n拋磚引玉，未來可以舉行︰<br />\n1. Stand with Journalist, Stand with Press集會 (針對警察侵犯第四權此事)<br />\n2. Connect全球不同宗教遊行(針對警方侮辱宗教)<br />\n3. 光復連儂牆行動(集會+文宣)<br />\n4. 守護投票站行動<br />\n<br />\n香港人最有創意，香港人最需要創意。<br />\n大家集思廣益<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/s0cSF6F.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fs0cSF6F.gif&h=32f64e29&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T09:02:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />旺角花園街條橋好多賓賓聚餐，我哋學下<br />\n狗到，就雙重標準，平時食環處理，上面吃野，馬路吃飽行下"},{"pid":"c03ae97b0037cecb0d541dfbfa0335700f3af098","tid":1689971,"uid":108757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1357e7172503cc63d62b4e02796bbbde2cd56a34","tid":1689971,"uid":55955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T08:40:27.000Z","msg":"新風向係叫人如果唔勇武就不如唔好做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T09:04:54.000Z","msg":"勇武都要創意，千篇一律俾人睇通晒點玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3dbf7c0fbadb4a5f042fdefa231ec7f166d9689","tid":1689971,"uid":11703,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T09:09:59.000Z","msg":"原來香港人反抗只係玩緊行為藝術<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n話畀你知個事實，雖然係難入耳啲<br />\n人數減少係因為睇唔到勝數<br />\n大部人仲未有覺悟咩叫真正嘅反抗"},{"pid":"bf5e0b12a91f80c99f29c7c52c16b486dc04f2f4","tid":1689971,"uid":35592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T09:11:56.000Z","msg":"習曱甴"},{"pid":"397042b7d7a01af53d233daffb1c5fc9dcf16c10","tid":1689971,"uid":38737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T09:14:34.000Z","msg":"推 真"},{"pid":"1a571813f9b773fab701575b07807421caf634b9","tid":1689971,"uid":258696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T09:16:01.000Z","msg":"勇武行動都要有新計劃先唔會比popo容易捉到啦 無可能一世停留6月陣地<br />\n和理非一樣需要有新玩法"},{"pid":"6f32a2d533567d70f913dd0ef8f2a00165786262","tid":1689971,"uid":4574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T09:16:04.000Z","msg":"有道理<br />\n<br />\n習曱甴"},{"pid":"74a67e270013c94da9d7aeff5f894b4c8fa2b9f4","tid":1689971,"uid":260814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T09:18:38.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1c10fefc7b22088df72b298cca00716991aea9cc","tid":1689971,"uid":165683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4ebce39454f